Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:06.41,biaoti,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\pos(316.43,936)\fad(400,400)}奴隶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,艾纳尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我才要说这话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,砍这种地方的树 你想把房子压垮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 你要当伐木工吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.85,0:03:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是战争 我在为战争训练
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 这威力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是块头大 在战场上派不上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,准备吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 别扔小刀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,扔盘子或者勺子不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,扔盘子你就愿意？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说 熊在入冬前必须吃很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 你怎么突然想起搞训练
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是为了保护这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这里被烧光 好不容易重建了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你们也不想再遇到那种事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,古斯姆家的牛奶就是好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那男人可不是一般地会摸奶子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你这动作好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:43.97,zhu,,0,0,0,,真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,算了吧算了吧 别跟战士扯上关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你就甘心总是输吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,老爸也是为了保护我们才死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,而你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,重建了村子 和两个美女共进美餐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有输
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,哟 还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:05:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你们听好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,进到林子里就向前狂奔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,然后沿着河跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,罗塔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,什么也不要想 笔直往前跑就行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥和妈妈都和你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:06:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,能行吗 我扶你起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,艾纳尔 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,把我丢下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,蠢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,别这么说 你加把劲站起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你真笨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 那边还有人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,还有女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来 艾纳尔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,快点带罗塔逃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,老妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是快死的老太婆 这点力气还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,只要活着…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就能再次…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.09,0:08:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,艾纳尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,罗塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,他们怎么不逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这姑娘还挺可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈死掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,罗塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,罗塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,放开罗塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.59,0:09:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,饶不了你 居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:40.14,zhu,,0,0,0,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,居然对哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙拿东西扎我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,把这小子卖了换酒钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走 酒钱
